con\" href=\"/images/6/64/Favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_levitation/zh-CN\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Potion_of_levitation_zh-CN rootpage-Potion_of_levitation skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Potion of levitation/zh-CN</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"><span class=\"subpages\">&lt; <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_levitation\" title=\"Potion of levitation\">Potion of levitation</a></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"width:50%;margin:auto;border:solid 3px #32CD32;background-color:#00FF00;text-align:center;clear:both\">\n<p><b>NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！</b><br />\n<a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN\" title=\"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\">了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"languages\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_levitation\" title=\"Potion of levitation\">English</a></b>\n<p><span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"zh-CN\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">中文（中国大陆）‎</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-brightmagenta\">!</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Pink_potion.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Pink potion.png\" src=\"/images/7/79/Pink_potion.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>飘浮\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"随机外观 (page does not exist)\">随机</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>200 <a href=\"/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"金币\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td>20\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>怪物使用\n</th>\n<td><small><i>不会被怪物使用。</i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>飘浮药水</b>（potion of levitation）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"药水\">药水</a>。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">消息</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#.E5.8F.A6.E8.AF.B7.E5.8F.82.E9.98.85\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">另请参阅</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B7%AB%E5%B8%88&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"巫师 (page does not exist)\">巫师</a>在游戏开始时获得的随机药水中有可能出现飘浮药水。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A5%AE%E7%94%A8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"饮用 (page does not exist)\">饮用</a>飘浮药水会令玩家获得持续一定时长的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"飘浮 (page does not exist)\">飘浮</a>特质，效果时长根据药水的<a href=\"/index.php?title=BUC/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"BUC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">BUC</a>而定：祝福的药水为250&#xff5e;299回合，未诅咒的药水为10&#xff5e;149回合，诅咒的药水不会延长玩家飘浮状态的时长。不论药水BUC如何，若玩家在饮用它时未飘浮，则会获得1回合的飘浮状态<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p><p>如果玩家在飘浮状态中饮用过祝福的飘浮药水，其可以随时输入<span class=\"kbd\"><span class=\"kbdsym\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B0%96%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%B7&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"尖括号 (page does not exist)\">&gt;</a></span></span>来立即结束当前的飘浮状态（除非有外在的飘浮来源），该效果在本次飘浮状态结束后即消失。\n</p><p>饮用诅咒的飘浮药水后：如果玩家在飘浮状态中，其会失去自由结束飘浮的能力；如果玩家不在飘浮状态，且不在上行<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%AF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"楼梯 (page does not exist)\">楼梯</a>处，则其会撞到天花板，并受到d10伤害（如果玩家穿戴非硬质<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%A4%B4%E7%9B%94\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"头盔\">头盔</a>，伤害降低到d6；如果玩家穿戴硬质头盔，则伤害降至d3）；如果玩家不在飘浮状态且在上行楼梯处，则其会飘到上一层。\n</p><p>将飘浮药水与<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"启蒙药水\">启蒙药水</a><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B5%B8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"浸 (page does not exist)\">混合</a>有<sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub>的概率<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"炼金术 (page does not exist)\">调制</a>出<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"升级药水 (page does not exist)\">升级药水</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>当你需要穿过某些会阻碍你前进的特殊地形时，该药水会很实用。以下是一些例子：\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%BE%8E%E6%9D%9C%E8%8E%8E%E5%B2%9B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"美杜莎岛 (page does not exist)\">美杜莎岛</a>，如果不想挖到下一层的话</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B0%94%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E4%BD%8D%E9%9D%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"气元素位面 (page does not exist)\">气元素位面</a>，有飘浮状态后你就可以自如活动了</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%81%AB%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E4%BD%8D%E9%9D%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"火元素位面 (page does not exist)\">火元素位面</a>，该层有大量<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%86%94%E5%B2%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"熔岩 (page does not exist)\">熔岩</a>地形</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%9C%B1%E6%AF%94%E7%83%88%E6%96%AF%E6%B2%BC%E6%B3%BD&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"朱比烈斯沼泽 (page does not exist)\">朱比烈斯沼泽</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%9F%8E%E5%A0%A1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"城堡 (page does not exist)\">城堡</a>的陷阱门走廊</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%A5%B3%E6%AD%A6%E7%A5%9E%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"女武神任务 (page does not exist)\">女武神任务</a>的部分楼层</li></ul>\n<p>在上述大多数场景下，若你有其他飘浮来源（例如<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE%E6%88%92%E6%8C%87&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"飘浮戒指 (page does not exist)\">飘浮戒指</a>），最好还是用其他飘浮来源而不是药水，这样可以把药水节省下来用于稀释或炼金术。不过，推荐留几瓶飘浮药水在气元素位面使用（如果你有探测魔法传送门的手段，一瓶药水甚至足够你通过气位面+火位面了），这样你可以省下一个戒指或靴子的装备槽。\n</p><p>用飘浮药水的另一个好处是你不用担心飘浮来源被偷走导致自身掉入水或熔岩里。戒指和靴子都会被<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%AD%85%E9%AD%94&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"魅魔 (page does not exist)\">魅魔</a>或<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E4%BB%99%E5%A5%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"仙女 (page does not exist)\">仙女</a>偷走，戒指会被电击摧毁，靴子会被施法怪物摧毁。不过，从另一角度来说，饮用祝福的飘浮药水也有误输入<span class=\"kbd\"><span class=\"kbdsym\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B0%96%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%B7&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"尖括号 (page does not exist)\">&gt;</a></span></span>导致直接中止飘浮并掉进水或熔岩的危险。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"消息\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\">消息</span></h2>\n<dl><dd><div class=\"noprint relarticle mainarticle\"><i>主条目：<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"飘浮 (page does not exist)\">飘浮#消息</a></i></div></dd>\n<dt><span id=\".E4.BD.A0.E7.89.87.E5.88.BB.E6.9C.89.E4.B8.80.E7.A7.8D.E7.A6.BB.E5.A5.87.E7.9A.84.E6.84.9F.E8.A7.89.EF.BC.8C.E7.84.B6.E5.90.8E.E6.B6.88.E9.80.80.E4.BA.86.E3.80.82\">你片刻有一种离奇的感觉，然后消退了。</span>（You have a peculiar feeling for a moment, then it passes.）</dt>\n<dd>药水是诅咒的，且你已处于飘浮状态，或位于水元素位面。</dd>\n<dt><span id=\".E4.BD.A0.E7.89.87.E5.88.BB.E6.9C.89.E4.B8.80.E7.A7.8D.E6.99.AE.E9.80.9A.E7.9A.84.E6.84.9F.E8.A7.89.EF.BC.8C.E7.84.B6.E5.90.8E.E6.B6.88.E9.80.80.E4.BA.86.E3.80.82\">你片刻有一种普通的感觉，然后消退了。</span>（You have a normal feeling for a moment, then it passes.）</dt>\n<dd>同上，但你处于幻觉状态。</dd>\n<dt><span id=\".E4.BD.A0.E7.9A.84.E6.92.9E.E5.88.B0.E4.BA.86.E3.80.82\">你的&lt;头&gt;撞到了&lt;天花板&gt;。</span>（You hit your &lt;head&gt; on the &lt;ceiling&gt;.）</dt>\n<dd>药水是诅咒的，你不处于飘浮状态，不位于水元素位面或上行楼梯。</dd></dl>\n<h2><span id=\"另请参阅\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8F.A6.E8.AF.B7.E5.8F.82.E9.98.85\">另请参阅</span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%E4%B9%A6&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"飘浮魔法书 (page does not exist)\">飘浮魔法书</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE%E9%9D%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"飘浮靴\">飘浮靴</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE%E6%88%92%E6%8C%87&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"飘浮戒指 (page does not exist)\">飘浮戒指</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.6_Released/src/potion.c#L1033\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.6, line 1033</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.6_Released/src/potion.c#L1067\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.6, line 1067</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.6_Released/src/potion.c#L1071\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.6, line 1071</a>\n     </span>